                        <interp inst="t18720819-name-464" type="given" value="COMISSIONER"></interp>MR. COMISSIONER KERR</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">left the case to the Jury; if they acquitted on the first Count, from the evidence of the marriage with the first wife, Watkins, that same evidence supported the second Count.</hi>
               </p>
